function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

}

// File added: 3p/symfony-mbstring-polyfill/LICENSE

	$tmp = pathinfo('3p/symfony-mbstring-polyfill/LICENSE');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/symfony-mbstring-polyfill/LICENSE')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('3p/symfony-mbstring-polyfill/LICENSE', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}

}

if (!is_file('3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html');
	writefile_14();
	if (!is_file('3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html') != '19e6aaa0e02c288eb17d018b226f19123a078054') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html') !== '19e6aaa0e02c288eb17d018b226f19123a078054') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html') !== 'f7d135fd1809f378a8d3ef8b9975342105cb452d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_14();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html') !== '19e6aaa0e02c288eb17d018b226f19123a078054') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/bignumber.js/doc/API.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/certs/cacert.pem')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/certs/cacert.pem');
	writefile_15();
	if (!is_file('3p/certs/cacert.pem')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/certs/cacert.pem');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/certs/cacert.pem') != '82fc9ac5a1fd4f55fa3d34d8da6b430d3ab1e7fc') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/certs/cacert.pem');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/certs/cacert.pem', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/certs/cacert.pem');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/certs/cacert.pem') !== '82fc9ac5a1fd4f55fa3d34d8da6b430d3ab1e7fc') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/certs/cacert.pem') !== 'ec7bb02ea174d6eeb433c0b3f6793c6c74a74139') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/certs/cacert.pem');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/certs/cacert.pem');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/certs/cacert.pem')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/certs/cacert.pem', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/certs/cacert.pem') !== '82fc9ac5a1fd4f55fa3d34d8da6b430d3ab1e7fc') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/certs/cacert.pem');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/jstree/jstree.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/jstree/jstree.js');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('3p/jstree/jstree.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/jstree/jstree.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.js') != '4790420abd787f8963d8ea3658ce699c38149030') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/jstree/jstree.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/jstree/jstree.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/jstree/jstree.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.js') !== '4790420abd787f8963d8ea3658ce699c38149030') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.js') !== 'f675bf2a9ba0a05b9da689d1f05b53556ac573d0') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/jstree/jstree.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/jstree/jstree.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/jstree/jstree.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/jstree/jstree.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.js') !== '4790420abd787f8963d8ea3658ce699c38149030') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/jstree/jstree.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
	writefile_17();
	if (!is_file('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js') != '01a9260933c07fccad2b68fbe1fe6e14321b29f6') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js') !== '01a9260933c07fccad2b68fbe1fe6e14321b29f6') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js') !== '7ee7168fd46455f0fd8bb237e6713eaa293e4b4c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_17();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js') !== '01a9260933c07fccad2b68fbe1fe6e14321b29f6') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
		}
	}
}

		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '548f34912e9fd5f8d88bfbdf1850f469da59a800') {

if (!is_file('oidplus.min.js.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: oidplus.min.js.php');
	writefile_20();
	if (!is_file('oidplus.min.js.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.min.js.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') != '4dbb30fc8c1a97e4f1e26f4875f7535cd8e96c73') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.js.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.min.js.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.min.js.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '4dbb30fc8c1a97e4f1e26f4875f7535cd8e96c73') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '242cdea577c149f2d1822d800321ae9e03d63a59') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.min.js.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.min.js.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.min.js.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.min.js.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_20();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '4dbb30fc8c1a97e4f1e26f4875f7535cd8e96c73') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.js.php');
		}
	}
}
